{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji49.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于国际形势的指示","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于国际形势的指示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1967年5月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说，美苏战略中心转移，我不赞成。他们是注意远东，但中心还在欧洲。欧洲七个师的兵力，并没有减少，只是调了几万老兵到远东。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":5}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":498,"page_end":498},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"世界形势","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"指示"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}